*** INDSTOCK.PRG

PROCEDURE INDSTOCK

CLEAR
@2,3 SAY "REGENERANDO INDICES..."

        USE STOCK

        REPLACE ALL PVIR WITH COSTE*1.08
        REPLACE ALL PVB WITH COSTE*1.3
        REPLACE ALL PVP WITH COSTE*1.4

        INDEX ON REF TO REF
        INDEX ON CLASE+COMENT1 TO CLASE

        USE

RETURN

